# Significant Changes Summary

> High-signal changelog. One entry per session, ordered newest-first. Append, never overwrite.

## Entry Format

```
### YYYY-MM-DD — [Session goal in a few words]

**Files changed:**
- `path/to/file` — what changed and why

**New features / fixes:**
- Bullet-list of user-visible changes

**Refactors / tech debt:**
- Structural changes not visible to end users

**Configuration / deployment:**
- Hermes config, env vars, docker, cron, etc.

**Revert / rollback note:**
- Anything that might need undoing
```

